">OFT</abbr>.</p>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Office of Fair Trading\">OFT</abbr> will consider if you&rsquo;re a &lsquo;fit person&rsquo; to have a licence. This includes looking at your past conduct and personal integrity. The <abbr title=\"Office of Fair Trading\">OFT</abbr> may consider that you&rsquo;re not a fit person if you or any of your associates have:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>breached the Consumer Credit Act or any other consumer protection law</li>\n  <li>committed a criminal offence involving fraud, dishonesty or violence</li>\n  <li>filed for insolvency or bankruptcy</li>\n  <li>been disqualified from being a director</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Office of Fair Trading\">OFT</abbr> has more information about the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.oft.gov.uk/OFTwork/credit-licensing/do-I-need\" title=\"Requirements for getting a licence\">requirements for getting a licence.</a></p>\n\n<h2>What you need a consumer credit licence for</h2>\n\n<p>You may need a licence if you:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>sell goods or services on credit (including hire purchase)</li>\n  <li>hire or lease out goods for more than 3 months</li>\n  <li>lend money</li>\n  <li>issue credit cards</li>\n  <li>arrange credit for other people</li>\n  <li>collect or purchase  consumer credit debts</li>\n  <li>give advice about people&rsquo;s credit rating</li>\n  <li>help people find and correct records about their financial standing</li>\n  <li>administer agreements for creditors or  assignees (but don&rsquo;t collect debts)</li>\n  <li>introduce customers to someone else who will lend them  money</li>\n  <li>help people with debt problems</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Any business offering credit or financing to customer must be licensed by the <abbr title=\"Office of Fair Trading\">OFT</abbr>, not just credit specialist companies. This includes non-profit organisations.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Business to business lending</h2>\n\n<p>You don&rsquo;t need to be licensed if you only offer credit to another business, unless your customer is: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>a sole trader</li>\n  <li>a partnership with fewer than 4 partners </li>\n  <li>an unincorporated association</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>If you offer credit to these customers, you&rsquo;re probably need a licence.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Credit reference agencies always need a licence, even if they only deal with businesses.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>About consumer credit law</h2>\n\n<p>Find out more about consumer credit law on the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.oft.gov.uk/about-the-oft/legal-powers/legal/cca/\" title=\"Consumer Credit Act\"><abbr title=\"Office of Fair Trading\">OFT</abbr> website.</a></p>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"short_description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null},{"title":"Sale of goods and services and data protection","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business%2Fsale-goods-services-data.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes regulations for online retailers, offering credit and Trading Standards","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business%2Fsale-goods-services-data","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business/sale-goods-services-data"},"parent":{"title":"Businesses and self-employed","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Information about starting up and running a business in the UK, including help if you're self employed or a sole trader.","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business"